snippet.title: Teeto - Gameplay Trailer [Feb 2025]
snippet.description:
Check out the brand new gameplay trailer for Teeto! With this new trailer also comes a significant demo update.

Teeto has undergone massive changes since it's last demo - introducing narrative elements, extra mechanics, reimagined levels and brand new content. 

Play the demo and wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2783370/Teeto/
